{
  "name": "Crown of Flame",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "type": "String",
      "label": "Description",
      "value": "<p>You channel Aqshy into a majestic crown of inspiring fire about your brow. You gain the @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.items.pTorrE0l3VybAbtn]{Fear (1)} Trait and @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.items.vCgEAetBMngR53aT]{War Leader} Talent  while the spell is active. For every +2 SL on your Casting Test, you may increase your Fear value by 1 or take the War Leader Talent again. Furthermore, gain a +10 bonus on all Channelling and Casting Tests using Aqshy while the spell is in effect.</p><p><strong>Lore:</strong> You may inflict +1 @Condition[Ablaze] Condition on anyone targeted by spells from the Lore of Fire, unless they also possess the Arcane Magic (Fire) Talent. Every Ablaze condition within Willpower Bonus yards adds +10 to attempts to Channel or Cast with Aqshy.</p><p></p>"
